title: TimWin's Game Suite 8.2
description:
ABOUT THIS GAME:

TimWin&#039;s Game Suite is a fun-filled collection of card games and
puzzles; BoxE, Go 4 Elevens!, 5 Hand Poker, Pick a Pair, Triple
Peaks, Flip Three, Poker Scramble, Rush to 21, Crazy 4 Eights
and Word Scramble. If you are a card player, or enjoy word
puzzles, download this game...you will not be disappointed.

Version 8.2 updates Internet links and is a bug fixing release.
